          function edgeRevert() {
            $(".edge-hide").css('transform', '');
            $(".edge-hide").removeClass('edge-hide');
          }

          function edgeZoom() {
            $(".edge-hide").css('transform', 'scale(2)');
            setTimeout(edgeRevert, 50);
          }

          function edgeSpriteFix(container) {
            if (navigator.userAgent.indexOf("Edge") == -1)
              return
            var selector = (container ? container + ' ' : '') + ".sprite"
            $(selector).addClass('edge-hide')
            setTimeout(edgeZoom, 10)
          }

        var itemPath = 'https://www.wowhead.com/item=';
        var npcPath = 'https://www.wowhead.com/npc=';
        var abilityCutoff = 10;
        var buffCutoff = 0;

                    function reformatForPTR(url) {
                const [protocol, rest] = url.split('//')
                const [wowhead, affix] = rest.replace('www.', '').split('/')

                return [
                    protocol,
                    [wowhead, 'beta', affix].join('/')
                ].join('//')
            }

            abilityPath = reformatForPTR(abilityPath);
            buffPath = reformatForPTR(buffPath);
            itemPath = reformatForPTR(itemPath);
            npcPath = reformatForPTR(npcPath);

            window.whPtrTooltipInterval = window.whPtrTooltipInterval || setInterval(() => {
                Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('a'))
                    .filter(a => a.href.includes('wowhead') && !a.href.includes('beta'))
                    .forEach(a => {
                        a.href = reformatForPTR(a.href);
                    });
            }, 1500);

        
        function abilityExternalLink(id) {
            if (id < abilityCutoff)
                return '#';
            if (buffCutoff && id >= buffCutoff)
                return buffPath + (id - buffCutoff);
            return abilityPath + id;
        }

        function abilityExternalLinkForEntry(ability) {
            let linkID = ability.secondaryGameID ? ability.secondaryGameID : ability.guid
            return abilityExternalLink(linkID)
        }

        function buffExternalLink(id) {
            if (id < abilityCutoff)
                return '#';
            if (buffCutoff)
                return `${buffPath}${id - buffCutoff}`;
            return `${buffPath}${id}`; // id can be a string for some games with no buff cutoff.
        }

        function buffExternalLinkForEntry(ability) {
            let linkID = ability.secondaryGameID ? ability.secondaryGameID : ability.guid
            return buffExternalLink(linkID)
        }

        function itemExternalLink(id) {
            return itemPath + id;
        }

        function npcExternalLink(id) {
            return npcPath + id;
        }

        function npcExternalLinkForEntry(actor) {
            let linkID = actor.secondaryGameID ? actor.secondaryGameID : actor.guid
            return npcExternalLink(linkID)
        }

    <script>
        function isClickOnMenu(event, classToLookFor, optionalClass) {
            const targetEvent = (event !== undefined && event !== null) ? event.target : null;
            if (targetEvent !== undefined && targetEvent !== null) {
                const parent = targetEvent.closest('.' + classToLookFor);
                const isClickInsideMenu = targetEvent.classList.contains(classToLookFor) ||
                    (parent !== null && parent !== undefined);
                if (!optionalClass) {
                    return isClickInsideMenu;
                } else {
                    const parentOptional = targetEvent.closest('.' + optionalClass);
                    const isClickInsideOptional = targetEvent.classList.contains(optionalClass) ||
                        (parentOptional !== null && parentOptional !== undefined);
                    return isClickInsideMenu || isClickInsideOptional;
                }
            } else {
                return true;
            }
            return false;
        }

        function openMenu(parentElementClassName, fadedPanelId, clickMenuTestFunction) {
            const parentElement = document.getElementsByClassName(parentElementClassName);
            if (parentElement !== undefined && parentElement !== null && parentElement.length > 0) {
                parentElement[0].classList.add("visible");
            }
            document.removeEventListener('click', onReportDocumentClick);
            document.getElementById(fadedPanelId).classList.add('open');
            document.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
                onReportDocumentClick(event, clickMenuTestFunction, parentElementClassName, fadedPanelId);
            });
        }

        function closeMenu(parentElementClassName, fadedPanelId) {
            const parentElement = document.getElementsByClassName(parentElementClassName);
            if (parentElement !== undefined && parentElement !== null && parentElement.length > 0) {
                parentElement[0].classList.remove("visible");
            }
            document.removeEventListener('click', onReportDocumentClick);
            document.getElementById(fadedPanelId).classList.remove('open');
        }

        function onReportDocumentClick(event, clickMenuTestFunction, parentElementClassName, fadedPanelId) {
            if (!clickMenuTestFunction(event)) {
                const guildOuterWrpList = document.getElementsByClassName(parentElementClassName);
                if (guildOuterWrpList !== undefined && guildOuterWrpList !== null && guildOuterWrpList.length > 0) {
                    closeMenu(parentElementClassName, fadedPanelId, this);
                }
            }
        }
    </script>

        <div class="report-bar-inset report-bar-inset-infos">

                                                            </script>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <script>
                    function onClickGuildElement(event) {
                        const guildOuterWrpList = document.getElementsByClassName('guild-reports-menu-outerWrp');
                        if (guildOuterWrpList !== undefined && guildOuterWrpList !== null && guildOuterWrpList.length > 0) {
                            if (guildOuterWrpList[0].classList.contains("visible")) {
                                if (isClickOnMenu(event, 'report-info-button')) {
                                    closeMenu('guild-reports-menu-outerWrp', 'report-view-contents');
                                    return false;
                                }
                            } else {
                                openMenu('guild-reports-menu-outerWrp', 'report-view-contents', isClickOnGuildMenu);
                            }
                        }
                    }

                    function isClickOnGuildMenu(event) {
                        return isClickOnMenu(event, 'report-info-title-wrp', 'report-info-button');
                    }
                </script>

                    <script>
                        function onClickSettingsButton(event) {
                            const guildOuterWrpList = document.getElementsByClassName('report-settings-dropdown');
                            if (guildOuterWrpList !== undefined && guildOuterWrpList !== null && guildOuterWrpList.length > 0) {
                                if (guildOuterWrpList[0].classList.contains("visible")) {
                                    if (isClickOnMenu(event, 'report-settings-btn')) {
                                        closeMenu('report-settings-dropdown', 'report-view-contents');
                                        return false;
                                    }
                                } else {
                                    openMenu('report-settings-dropdown', 'report-view-contents', isClickOnSettingsMenu);
                                }
                            }
                        }

                        function isClickOnSettingsMenu(event) {
                            return isClickOnMenu(event, 'report-settings', 'report-settings-btn');
                        }

                            onClickSettingsButton(event)

                                                    <a href="#" class="filter-type-tab drop selected" id="filter-casts-tab" onclick="return changeFilterType('casts', this)" oncontextmenu="changeFilterType('casts', this)">Casts</a>
                        
                        <div style="clear:both"></div>
                    </div>

                </div>
                            </div>

                    <p>Or you can search for parses similar to yours using the options below:</p>
                    <table cellspacing="10">
                        <tbody><tr>
                            <td nowrap="">Select Player:
                            </td><td>
                                <ul id="compare-selection-dropdown" class="compare-selection-menu sm sm-black" data-smartmenus-id="17201093130190876">
                                    <li><a href="#" onclick="return dropdownClicked(this, event)" class="has-submenu"><span class="sub-arrow">+</span><span id="compare-selection-text">Select a Player</span></a>
                                        <ul id="compare-selection-container"></ul>
                                </li></ul>
                        </td></tr><tr>
                            <td nowrap="">Fight Length:
                            </td><td>Limit the search to fights whose duration is within <input type="text" class="compare-number" value="10" id="compare-duration-delta">
                                seconds of this fight. This value only applies to kills.
                                                    </td></tr><tr>
                                <td nowrap="">Raid Size:
                                </td><td>Limit the raid size to a difference of no more than <input type="text" class="compare-number" value="2" id="compare-size-delta">
                                    players.
                            </td></tr><tr>
                                <td nowrap="">Item Level:
                                </td><td>Limit search to parses within <input type="text" class="compare-number" value="2" id="compare-ilvl-delta"> item level(s) of the
                                    selected player (or the fight's average item level if a fight is selected).
                                                            </td></tr><tr>
                            <td nowrap="">Time Range:
                            </td><td>Limit search to parses that occurred within the last <input type="text" class="compare-number" value="28" id="compare-date-delta">

<script>
function deferredTooltipInitialization1For0(idToUse)
{
    if (!tooltipsInitialized[1-0])
        tooltipsInitialized[1-0] = [];
    if (tooltipsInitialized[1-0][idToUse])
        return
    tooltipsInitialized[1-0][idToUse] = 1

    if (idToUse === "main-table-link") {
        initTable('#popup-table-ability-9-0-1', 'simple');
        initTable('#popup-table-source-9-0-1', 'simple');
        initTable('#popup-table-target-9-0-1', 'simple');
        createTipped("#main-table-row-9-0-1 .main-table-link", $("#popup-tooltip-9-0-1")[0]);
        Tipped.show("#main-table-row-9-0-1 .main-table-link")
        return
    }



    if (idToUse === "main-table-amount") {


        return
    }









}
</script>

<script>
function deferredTooltipInitialization2For0(idToUse)
{
    if (!tooltipsInitialized[2-0])
        tooltipsInitialized[2-0] = [];
    if (tooltipsInitialized[2-0][idToUse])
        return
    tooltipsInitialized[2-0][idToUse] = 1

    if (idToUse === "main-table-link") {
        initTable('#popup-table-ability-192-0-2', 'simple');
        initTable('#popup-table-source-192-0-2', 'simple');
        initTable('#popup-table-target-192-0-2', 'simple');
        createTipped("#main-table-row-192-0-2 .main-table-link", $("#popup-tooltip-192-0-2")[0]);
        Tipped.show("#main-table-row-192-0-2 .main-table-link")
        return
    }



    if (idToUse === "main-table-amount") {


        return
    }

    if (idToUse === "main-table-active") {
        createTipped("#main-table-row-192-0-2 .main-table-active", $("#popup-tooltip-active-192-0-2")[0]);
        Tipped.show("#main-table-row-192-0-2 .main-table-active")
        return
    }








}
</script>

    if (idToUse === "main-table-active") {
        createTipped("#main-table-row-200-0-23 .main-table-active", $("#popup-tooltip-active-200-0-23")[0]);
        Tipped.show("#main-table-row-200-0-23 .main-table-active")
        return
    }








}
</script>

Your profile can be used (also later) to present content that appears more relevant based on your possible interests, such as by adapting the order in which content is shown to you, so that it is even easier for you to find content that matches your interests.</p><a class="fc-purpose-feature-more-info" role="button" aria-label="View details, Create profiles to personalise content" tabindex="0" data-purpose-id="5" data-name="Create profiles to personalise content" href="#">View details</a></div><label class="fc-preference-slider-container fc-consent-preference-container"><span class="fc-preference-slider-label">Consent (83 vendors)</span><span class="fc-preference-slider"><input type="checkbox" role="button" aria-label="Consent (83 vendors), Create profiles to personalise content" aria-pressed="false" tabindex="0" class="fc-preference-consent purpose" data-id="5"><span class="fc-slider-el"></span></span></label></div><div class="fc-preference-container"><div class="fc-preference-title"><h2>Use profiles to select personalised content</h2></div><div class="fc-preference-description"><p class="fc-purpose-feature-description fc-truncated-3-line">Content presented to you on this service can be based on your content personalisation profiles, which can reflect your activity on this or other services (for instance, the forms you submit, content you look at), possible interests and personal aspects.
